- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the cognitive processes involved in communication and language understanding.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper describes cognitive models of situated embodied agents, which are a common topic in AI research.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is relevant as the experiments involve robotic agents and their ability to communicate about spatial information.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is possible as the paper may involve machine learning techniques for the cognitive models.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve analyzing the computational complexity of the cognitive models.
